m-4" href="https://dxp.rsna.org/user/index.html" tabindex="" class="nav-link text-small-bold">Diagnosis Please</a></li><li class="nav-item pr-xl-24"><div class="dropdown"><a id="publication-menu-item-5" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-small-bold">Multimedia</a><div aria-labelledby="publication-menu-item-5" class="dropdown-menu"><a href="/page/podcasts#radiology" class="dropdown-item">Podcasts</a><a href="/action/doSearch?=&amp;startPage=&amp;target=digital-object-search&amp;DOResourceTypeId=tweetorial&amp;sortBy=PubDateField_desc" class="dropdown-item">Tweetorials</a><a href="/action/doSearch?=&amp;startPage=&amp;target=digital-object-search&amp;DOResourceTypeId=video&amp;sortBy=PubDateField_desc" class="dropdown-item">Video Summaries</a></div></div></li><li class="nav-item pr-xl-24"><div class="dropdown"><a id="publication-menu-item-6" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-small-bold">Information</a><div aria-labelledby="publication-menu-item-6" class="dropdown-menu"><a href="/page/radiology/about" class="dropdown-item">About Radiology</a><a href="/page/radiology/about#citation_metrics" class="dropdown-item">Citation Metrics</a><a href="/page/radiology/edboard" class="dropdown-item">Editorial Board</a><a href="/page/radiology/radintraining/edboard" class="dropdown-item">Trainee Editorial Board</a><a href="/page/radiology/margulis" class="dropdown-item">Margulis Award</a></div></div></li></ul></div><div class="publication__menu__content__links d-flex flex-column align-items-xl-center flex-xl-row"></div></div><a data-toggle="collapse" href="#publication__menu__content" role="button" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="header-side-menu" class="sidebar__overlay"></a></div></nav>
